[Rewrite]
#开屏广告｜开屏歌曲热评｜搜索页下方横幅广告
^https?:\/\/(interface3?\.music\.163\.com|[\d\.]+)\/eapi\/ad reject-dict

#播放页歌名下方∶乐迷团｜关注｜播放页提示｜音乐应用红点｜播放提示?
^https?:\/\/(interface3?\.music\.163\.com|[\d\.]+)\/eapi\/(community\/friends\/fans-group\/artist\/group\/get|user\/sub\/artist|music\/songshare\/text\/recommend\/get|mine\/applet\/redpoint|resniche\/position\/play\/new\/get) reject-dict

#评论区插入广告｜回复广告｜首页右上角免或vip图标｜播放页的各种小提示｜评论右上角热评馆｜播放页正在试听弹窗｜播放页右上角live或直播图标入口｜首次登录黑胶过期弹窗   new resource
^https?:\/\/(interface3?\.music\.163\.com|[\d\.]+)\/eapi\/(comment\/feed\/inserted|v\d\/content\/exposure\/comment\/banner|link\/(position\/show\/(strategy|resource)|scene\/show)|comment\/hotcomment\/collect|vipcenter\/tspopup\/get|mlivestream\/entrance\/playpage|vipauth\/app\/auth|music-vip-membership\/client\/vip\/info) reject-dict

# 搜索页热搜卡片｜猜你喜欢｜我的应用下方提醒
^https?:\/\/(interface3?\.music\.163\.com|[\d\.]+)\/w?e?api\/(search\/(chart|default|rcmd\/keyword|specialkeyword)|(resource-exposure\/|middle\/clientcfg\/config)|activity\/bonus\/playpage\/time\/query) reject-dict

